transcription.text: Designed and painted by 'Prisoner: Cell Block H' fan Greig Chambers and sculpted by Jason Miller. This set, made especially for ACMI Renewal - Moving Australia, includes figurines of characters Bea, Lizzie, Rita, Vera and Joan as well as set pieces: 2 brick wall pieces, 3 sets of bars and 1 prison door. These are not commercially available.
